[SN]TITLE[SN]
French kids tell us their thoughts on Euro 2016

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Today is a massive day in the world of football - it's the start of Euro 2016.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
10 June 2016 Last updated at 11:49 BST
24 teams will compete to be crowned European Champions, starting with hosts France playing Romania on Friday evening.
Newsround has been speaking to some local kids in Bordeaux in the build up to the big opening match.
